text: The Centre hospitalier intercommunal de Poissy-Saint-Germain-en-Laye is a well-known hospital in the Poissy and Saint-Germain-en-Laye, close to Paris. It was created in 1997.Poissy-Saint Germain-en-Laye : l'hôpital du futur sur les rails It is partner of the Université de Versailles Saint-Quentin-en- Yvelines.UFR Simone Veil - santé == References == == Further reading == * CHIPS Category:1997 establishments in France Category:University hospitals in France Category:Yvelines
